Introduction

Astell was a South Korean girl group under Errday. They made their debut on July 9, 2024, with the digital single "ISLAND." On December 20, 2024, Errday announced the termination of the members' exclusive artist contract and announced in the same statement that the members had signed new contracts with Midas Entertainment.
